{"tid":1133782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攻陷貝澳營地插針式紮營　中國遊客連沙灘都不放過","createTime":"2019-05-01T10:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T02:35:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":358,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"70d61a840722e68d696ee8e3e67616ead49704da","tid":1133782,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190501/photo/bkn-20190501173419042-0501_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190501182051\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190501%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190501173419042-0501_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190501182051&h=aa276826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以往內地旅客愛趁假期到港購物，近年卻逐漸攻陷郊區。東網記者今日(1日)到貝澳營地視察，發現營區完全爆滿，幾乎全是內地遊客，猶如置身內地，附近草地8成空間亦已「插針式」紮滿帳篷，部分更犯禁在沙灘上紮營。有常到貝澳紮營的內地遊客指，7、8年前大多都是本地人，近年幾乎都是內地人，「都是講普通話」。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，內地露營客多帶備行李箱，又自備食材。深圳旅客林先生與王先生結伴到貝澳紮營，林指自己每隔2年便來，今次已是第4次到貝澳紮營，有感環境優美，配套完善，營友十分親切。林指，2012年首次來紮營時基本上都是本地人，但近年內地人愈來愈多。<br />\n<br />\n內地遊客徐先生一行17人到貝澳露營，他表示香港市區已失去吸引力，「第一次比較新鮮，第二、三次都一樣，和現在深圳差不多」。他指，在網上看到介紹，稱貝澳是香港「五星級露營地」，來到發現比想像中還要好，亦比較划算，已帶備米及其他食糧。<br />\n<br />\n另一內地遊客凡女士則指，自己與9名親友同行，其中5個是小朋友。她表示露營比較適合親子活動，貝澳配套完善又安全，而所有工具及食材都是從內地帶過來，「只需要付交通費」，十分划算。她指一行人打算住2、3天，渡過五一長假。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190501/photo/bkn-20190501173419042-0501_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190501182051\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190501%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190501173419042-0501_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190501182051&h=1edd94ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190501/photo/bkn-20190501173419042-0501_00822_001_03b.jpg?20190501182051\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190501%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190501173419042-0501_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20190501182051&h=9ff8f18c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190501/photo/bkn-20190501173419042-0501_00822_001_04b.jpg?20190501182051\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190501%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190501173419042-0501_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20190501182051&h=aee0c6fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190501/bkn-20190501173419042-0501_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190501%2Fbkn-20190501173419042-0501_00822_001.html&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=677cb570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190501/bkn-20190501173419042-0501_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b1fb04950c01b6f4a63605c4f0894ed4ba270b5e","tid":1133782,"uid":30966,"like":263,"dislike":1,"score":262,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:34:05.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲冇話錯"},{"pid":"26de7ab713b609ca331dbe2698130cad37b0b487","tid":1133782,"uid":26578,"like":316,"dislike":2,"score":314,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"啲蝗蟲究竟幾時死"},{"pid":"20b8433624a770bc23c9518aa41943c3321c9d36","tid":1133782,"uid":40470,"like":288,"dislike":1,"score":287,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:36:59.000Z","msg":"有無巴打半夜去夾band?"},{"pid":"4c26f788a96363a206d55f026820c32335483e06","tid":1133782,"uid":3189,"like":134,"dislike":1,"score":133,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"咁樣密密麻麻紮營有咩樂趣......?"},{"pid":"ad5190d6d30d09c9d898bfcbb50fd0379da8d14c","tid":1133782,"uid":237425,"like":229,"dislike":1,"score":228,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:39:45.000Z","msg":"沙灘好多沙蚤架wo, 咬到仆街<br />\n支那人果然CLS"},{"pid":"f7c9a2a4f20536632ba0490baabef9ac6e9968d7","tid":1133782,"uid":28695,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"係正禁止牌隔離都無人趕?"},{"pid":"275720fd2408842df2c93725a0ffccd0acc48b48","tid":1133782,"uid":7057,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"搞到成個難民營咁"},{"pid"